{"tid":691293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要變中國台灣了！　澳航執行長：將遵守中國民航局要求  原文網址: 要變中國台灣了！　澳航執行長：將遵守中國民航局要求","createTime":"2018-06-05T14:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T03:53:04.000Z","uid":156815,"like":9,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6ebb049c7e3f9a7ef48c11bfde855e4078eeb278","tid":691293,"uid":156815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"中國民航局日前發函給全球航空公司，要求不得將台、港、澳標示為獨立國家，全球20間航空公司迫於壓力照辦。原本不願改變的澳洲航空（Qantas Airways），執行長喬伊斯（Alan Joyce）4日也宣布將依循中國航空監管機構的要求更改。<br />\n<br />\n綜合澳洲媒體報導，澳洲航空執行長喬伊斯於雪梨國際航空運輸協會（International Air Transport Association，IATA）上表示，公司計畫將遵守中國民航局的要求，將台灣標示成其領地，但需要時間進行，「我們的想法是會達成要求，但完成前會需要一些時間」。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲外交部長畢紹普（Julie Bishop）先前曾向北京當局喊話，澳洲當局依然堅持「一個中國」的原則，但國內私營企業屬於「自家事務」，不應該受到政府的壓力而運行，「不管是我們的（政府），或是其他國家的（政府），此舉都會威脅到企業的日常營運。」<br />\n<br />\n根據美國《外交政策》雜誌，美國航空與聯合航空等多家航空公司都曾收到類似信函，信中指出，若不配合「一個中國」原則，那麼公司網站可能遭到封鎖，進而喪失對國際航空公司而言最重要的中國市場。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸民航局4月發函，要求全球44家航空公司必須遵守一中原則，將台灣、香港、澳門從國家，改列為地區並加註中國；截至5月25日已有18家完成更改，26家承諾整改，而預計完成時間最早為5月28日，最晚為7月25日。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180605/1184117.htm#ixzz5HYyNJ0la \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180605%2F1184117.htm%23ixzz5HYyNJ0la%20&d=mbGP7JXlvFSBBMzyTBH6yGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d35823a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180605/1184117.htm#ixzz5HYyNJ0la </a><br />\n<br />\n中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"ad23fa4e563384bc6371e513dd235cf07f408af6","tid":691293,"uid":156815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"有錢真係大撚曬"},{"pid":"034848b7805c113a194ead4ec5b009d5ac069211","tid":691293,"uid":119778,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"班台仔仲日日笑鳩中國人香港"},{"pid":"592544dcef5ee8a513533f151d45eacdbe017b2a","tid":691293,"uid":119778,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班台仔仲日日笑鳩中國香港</blockquote>"},{"pid":"85a60f2f2e131649541f6b8777e2f4e4a9d35bca","tid":691293,"uid":179938,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:03:54.000Z","msg":"成撚日咩一中一中，<br />\n一個香港，一個中國，一個台灣，有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90218d1e2c17eb03e595fb11900e607540ff6d49","tid":691293,"uid":83097,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"搭左無數次qantas<br />\n估唔到始終要轉返坐CX <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce4be75de40b9742d6e0f303bd7d646740d8e17","tid":691293,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"台仔比人杯死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e149e98fe64cf1709340672f57b97cfcef52b1a1","tid":691293,"uid":34103,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ee7d172af7ebd045dd62f50f475f716d5a1dd55","tid":691293,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 何東妹"},{"pid":"daa693c0e4c76068f6c357ae3ac6e43662aa8dc4","tid":691293,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:07:49.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"f2fee7b4b972f81daf78b93393e60d085f75dbdd","tid":691293,"uid":100276,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"支那國跟本已經係邪惡核心國，比伊朗，俄羅斯更卑鄙，用錢來破壞你文明社會核心價值"},{"pid":"44599d9ffb3d2b5656fa101c8b23a765b6c16335","tid":691293,"uid":156815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:09:34.000Z","msg":"笑鳩台灣有意思咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重點係支那既惡行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"